{"tid":1461470,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"注意！我地已緊急將大量文宣片上線，務求傳到香港每個角落，世界每一處！要讓真相道出！","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T08:55:39.000Z","uid":1806,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"38ea069fa14ecd51e2c2c70ea880b0b6d251ec21","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>致各位巴絲</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝巴絲們嘅勇躍支持同加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，讓我們以最快速度完成擴展團隊，繼續製作更多更高質更多元化嘅文宣片俾香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同時我地向各位未能加入既熱心巴絲講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望在將來再次擴展團隊時，能夠同你地合作，做得更好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港警察自6月開始不綁以過度武力對待示威者及違犯一系列守則與法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，更越趨嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，已去到文明社會下不可接受既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時暴政及警方更每天企圖以不同方式狡辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，意圖混淆視線，誤導市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對於近日8月11日警察既所作所為泯滅人性，完全令人髮指，孰不可忍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝各文宣組設計同分享各種文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我們團隊手足已急速趕製各類型文宣片反擊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">包括已出811 同812 既片</span>，上載至Facebook, YouTube 及 Instagram</span></strong>，但最重要既事係需要大家既支持同傳閱俾身邊既人, 特別仍然係中立同淺藍人士收看。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我地團隊希望得到巴絲們既支持，如果可以...</strong><br />\n<blockquote><strong>Like FB Page - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=7a2f359c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV</a><br />\nFollow IG - <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkgetv&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=098f4aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkgetv</a><br />\nSubscribe Youtube Channel <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=ae0a94e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w</a> </strong></blockquote><br />\n<strong>咁就好啦，多謝各位</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，由於時間關係，人手安排同重組，近日未有英文及外語片，我地會加緊製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港警察近期暴行記事簿 (7月21日至8月11日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MrugpgfkvDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMrugpgfkvDs&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=f21e4aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MrugpgfkvDs</a><br />\n<br />\n8月11日發生了什麼事之懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RvP84cf2x4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRvP84cf2x4k&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c212dbd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RvP84cf2x4k</a><br />\n<br />\n8.12 香港機場集會紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Mb8Z3MFCPk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Mb8Z3MFCPk&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e336fe8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Mb8Z3MFCPk</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中黑白大字報 - 警察篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8_bqouuRhJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8_bqouuRhJ8&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=3e47c0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8_bqouuRhJ8</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n其他近日製作的片將會係下一個Post 繼續展示<br />\n如果有咩建議，歡迎提出，再次多謝大家既支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命! </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7ab02b30285f5d8e2732bb5f2464fec90ca19d74","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>林鄭想同香港玉石俱焚? 其實班抗爭者好可愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SjaSEU7QymY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSjaSEU7QymY&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=49f3d784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SjaSEU7QymY</a><br />\n<br />\n8.05 三罷集會 - 沙田紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qDocYyeS8vM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqDocYyeS8vM&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=daa27282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qDocYyeS8vM</a><br />\n<br />\n8.10 「守護孩子未來」親子遊行紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GAnI8nD8AMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGAnI8nD8AMQ&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c39d9f7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GAnI8nD8AMQ</a><br />\n<br />\n一封機動部隊太太的信及一名市民太太的回覆<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wls50_Fbc40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWls50_Fbc40&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=ff4f8422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wls50_Fbc40</a></strong>"},{"pid":"eb95cc199ac6d2e8b4c9a268f41b0c7eec01c6d6","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e813b07691297af07c48d7348d6ccc03c68ad9","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2bf84b41859f24758eb2ca0f01795fbe87cd60","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cbcae0978cff28133a8b4dedbbc79c8b6ee82b","tid":1461470,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"145fb28acf413070e59c4bd4f24de930be581089","tid":1461470,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35d39173758a6c6d4f8ca35c41e8a2f67aa3c921","tid":1461470,"uid":165925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">部分示威者停止暴力衝擊<br />\n部分黑警察停止濫用武力<br />\n政府作出讓步並不再企硬<br />\n歡迎和理非繼續合法示威</span></span><br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落同時請考慮每個行動既利與弊<br />\n否則恐怕變成文革2.0<br />\n目標稍有雜質 <br />\n大家就骨牌效應集體做偏左<br />\n花你搭車痾屎時間去重溫<br />\n鏗鏘集：文革五十年（上）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZOqrQnxq0jA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=963f6851\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA</a><br />\n<br />\n「團結」雖是美德，但亦係雙刃劍<br />\n<br />\nBe water, be considerate, be safe."},{"pid":"43bc21fb8582e5f9fe8e06f1e427f0380118fe55","tid":1461470,"uid":39042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a602e07a5b813280595d883ebecc295f425667fa","tid":1461470,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9e4bd05f55c82181badd3578f7136adf3f806e33","tid":1461470,"uid":261406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cd48d60f75fd9367d895eb07491eee00a765511","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640f2eacd13e2db36050f72644224b52a934da7d","tid":1461470,"uid":168188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f581135beb67c07084a928fafb060d30005ae345","tid":1461470,"uid":152108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a15e4bf92a4b223519be563cbfb9dac084a39b05","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50436ceca5bce7