:260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"fb51e5e19a3faede5a9b5cc4388356f4a2600fe7","tid":1461470,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ea069fa14ecd51e2c2c70ea880b0b6d251ec21","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>致各位巴絲</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝巴絲們嘅勇躍支持同加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，讓我們以最快速度完成擴展團隊，繼續製作更多更高質更多元化嘅文宣片俾香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同時我地向各位未能加入既熱心巴絲講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望在將來再次擴展團隊時，能夠同你地合作，做得更好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港警察自6月開始不綁以過度武力對待示威者及違犯一系列守則與法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，更越趨嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，已去到文明社會下不可接受既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時暴政及警方更每天企圖以不同方式狡辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，意圖混淆視線，誤導市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對於近日8月11日警察既所作所為泯滅人性，完全令人髮指，孰不可忍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝各文宣組設計同分享各種文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我們團隊手足已急速趕製各類型文宣片反擊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">包括已出811 同812 既片</span>，上載至Facebook, YouTube 及 Instagram</span></strong>，但最重要既事係需要大家既支持同傳閱俾身邊既人, 特別仍然係中立同淺藍人士收看。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我地團隊希望得到巴絲們既支持，如果可以...</strong><br />\n<blockquote><strong>Like FB Page - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=7a2f359c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV</a><br />\nFollow IG - <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkgetv&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=098f4aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkgetv</a><br />\nSubscribe Youtube Channel <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=ae0a94e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w</a> </strong></blockquote><br />\n<strong>咁就好啦，多謝各位</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，由於時間關係，人手安排同重組，近日未有英文及外語片，我地會加緊製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港警察近期暴行記事簿 (7月21日至8月11日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MrugpgfkvDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMrugpgfkvDs&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=f21e4aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MrugpgfkvDs</a><br />\n<br />\n8月11日發生了什麼事之懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RvP84cf2x4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRvP84cf2x4k&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c212dbd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RvP84cf2x4k</a><br />\n<br />\n8.12 香港機場集會紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Mb8Z3MFCPk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Mb8Z3MFCPk&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e336fe8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Mb8Z3MFCPk</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中黑白大字報 - 警察篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8_bqouuRhJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8_bqouuRhJ8&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=3e47c0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8_bqouuRhJ8</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n其他近日製作的片將會係下一個Post 繼續展示<br />\n如果有咩建議，歡迎提出，再次多謝大家既支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命! </span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"文宣可以加下面三件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要令黑警變不可信證人<br />\n我係一位EMAIL左各泛民議員懇請搞818遊行同聯署既網民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461052</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/size=2]<br />\n<br />\n有冇人fc到？示威者被捕後被打至脊髓壓迫？仲有多人被打同屈到多處骨折？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［突發］被捕者媽媽網上指兒子入警署後被打至腦出血！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb9b8d9e948cbf01a815fb8c05d42cb4bf22fc04","tid":1461470,"uid":259154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2f7b4e9a1ccdbbf3d2d943c9b43d99bd5c976f","tid":1461470,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.